                <p><lb 
                    n="1"/>sidhaṁ vāniyasa kuṭasa sa<lb 
                    n="2" break="no"/>bhariyasa saputakasa saduhu<lb 
                    n="3" break="no"/>tukasa sanatukasa dakhināyā<lb 
                    n="4" break="no"/>ke cetiyakhabho sadhāduko dānaṁ
                </p>
            </div>
