            <div type="translation" resp="part:argr part:inst part:vito">
                <p>Success! A <foreign>caitya</foreign><supplied reason="subaudible">-bearing</supplied> pillar, containing relics, <supplied reason="subaudible">erected</supplied> on the southern <placeName type="builtPlace"><foreign>āyāka</foreign></placeName>: the gift of the merchant <persName type="human"><roleName type="merchant" subtype="donor">Kuṭa</roleName></persName>, together with his wife, son<supplied reason="subaudible">s</supplied>, daughter<supplied reason="subaudible">s</supplied>, and grandchildren.</p>
            </div>
